+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: LGPL-2.1 OR MIT */
+/*
+ * Author: Paul Burton <paul.burton@mips.com>
+ * (C) Copyright 2018 MIPS Tech LLC
+ * (C) Copyright 2016-2022 - Mathieu Desnoyers <mathieu.desnoyers@efficios.com>
